{"type":"message","id":"f84a6b82","parentId":"0066224e","timestamp":"2026-05-02T10:38:47.770Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"After the restart, I should let Bobby know what's happening and what I found. The issue is that MiniMax M2.7 isn't responding fast enough for the email check and morning brief jobs - both have extremely complex prompts with lots of tools. The timeout is happening because the model is slow to respond and the idle timeout kicks in.\n\nThe email check ran for 285+ seconds (nearly 5 minutes) before timing out. The morning brief ran for 144 seconds before timing out.\n\nLet me explain this to Bobby clearly.\n","thinkingSignature":"d14bfc14c09b5b8fae01454473569bd7c9e0bb5991b04005ab7e5129207f6577"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nHey Bobby! I found the issue — your **Emmy Email Check** and **Morning Brief** cron jobs are timing out. The error says:\n\n> \"The model did not produce a response before the model idle timeout\"\n\n**What's happening:** These jobs are running fine, but they're doing a LOT of work (checking Gmail, iCloud, calendar, weather, etc.) and the MiniMax model is taking longer than expected to process everything and generate a response. The system has a built-in idle timeout that's being hit before the model finishes.\n\n**The email check ran for ~4.7 minutes** before timing out — it was probably actually working, just slow. **The morning brief timed out after ~2.4 minutes.**\n\nI just restarted the gateway to clear any stuck state, but if timeouts keep happening, there are a few options:\n1. **Increase the timeout** for the MiniMax provider (I'd need to add a config setting for this)\n2. **Simplify the email check prompt** so it does less work per run\n3. **Switch to a faster model** for cron jobs (like Grok 4.1 Fast which is already configured)\n\nWant me to look into increasing the timeout or simplifying those job prompts?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":198,"output":361,"cacheRead":56320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56879,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777718319159,"responseId":"0645072f315cc9c7b5fbd2ede2e42423"}}
