{"type":"message","id":"3fd63f9f","parentId":"6b840b0d","timestamp":"2026-05-02T15:00:47.915Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the cron job to use the skill instead of the long step-by-step prompt. I'll update the message payload to something much simpler that references the skill.\n","thinkingSignature":"c6403e7902b0ac87cbd0a7678121dd75496bed261b2e7a9822b86bd7ebf686e7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nUpdated! Now let me simplify the cron job to use the skill instead of that long step-by-step script:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i4ty7pzs0gqo_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1451,"output":81,"cacheRead":52736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54268,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777734045940,"responseId":"0645449e86ce156a43d2d7f90771641c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"66a5f94b","parentId":"3fd63f9f","timestamp":"2026-05-02T15:00:48.353Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i4ty7pzs0gqo_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\",\n      \"agentId\": \"emmy\",\n      \"name\": \"Emmy Email Check\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773960428074,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 3600000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1773961081922\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Check for new emails in Bobby's Gmail AND iCloud accounts. Send TWO separate Telegram messages — one for Gmail, one for iCloud.\\n\\n=== GMAIL CHECK ===\\nSTEP 1: Read the last timestamp file:\\nLAST_CHECK=$(cat /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp 2>/dev/null)\\nIf the file doesn't exist or is empty, set LAST_CHECK to 0.\\n\\nSTEP 2: Search Gmail for ALL unread inbox emails (no time limit — we filter by timestamp below):\\ngog gmail search 'in:inbox is:unread' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 3: For each email found:\\n- Read the email to get its full content: gog gmail get <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n- Get the email's internalDate (Unix timestamp when Gmail received it)\\n- ONLY process if internalDate > LAST_CHECK (email arrived AFTER the last check)\\n- Skip emails where internalDate <= LAST_CHECK (already reported)\\n\\nSTEP 4: Also search Unroll.me/Unsubscribed:\\ngog gmail search 'label:\\\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed\\\" newer_than:1d' --max 20 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\\nFor any found, move to INBOX: gog gmail batch modify <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com --remove \\\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed,CATEGORY_PROMOTIONS\\\" --add INBOX\\n\\nSTEP 5: Categorize each NEW email (only those with internalDate > LAST_CHECK):\\n  🔴 Bills/Payments — financial obligations, bills, due dates, bank alerts, payments (Capital One, KUB, Flex, Affirm, Netflix, etc.)\\n  🟡 Orders — shipping confirmations, receipts, order updates\\n  🔵 Updates — service notifications, security alerts, account changes\\n  ⚪ Low Priority — newsletters, promotions, marketing, social media\\n\\nSTEP 6: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for Gmail:\\nIf NEW emails (internalDate > LAST_CHECK):\\n📬 GMAIL — X new email(s)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [1-line snippet from email body]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [1-line snippet]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [1-line snippet]\\n\\nIf NO new emails (all unread emails were <= LAST_CHECK): \\\"📬 GMAIL — No new emails\\\"\\n\\nSTEP 7: Update timestamp AFTER sending the report:\\necho $(date +%s) > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp\\n\\n=== ICLOUD CHECK ===\\nSTEP 8: Get iCloud credentials:\\nICLOUD_CREDS=$(security find-generic-password -a \\\"rtg.bobby@icloud.com\\\" -s \\\"emmy-icloud-email\\\" -w 2>/dev/null)\\n\\nSTEP 9: Search iCloud INBOX for unseen emails:\\ncurl -s --url \\\"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\\\" --user \\\"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\\\" -X \\\"SEARCH UNSEEN\\\" 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 10: Get full envelope for new messages:\\ncurl -s --url \\\"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\\\" --user \\\"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\\\" -X \\\"FETCH <msg_num>:* (ENVELOPE)\\\" 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 11: Track with checkpoint file:\\nLAST_ICLOUD=$(cat /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"0\\\")\\n- Only process messages with msg_num > LAST_ICLOUD\\n- After processing, update: echo <highest_msg_num> > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt\\n\\nSTEP 12: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for iCloud:\\nIf new: \\\"📬 ICLOUD — X new email(s)\\\\n\\\\n[Sender — Subject]\\\"\\nIf none: \\\"📬 ICLOUD — No new emails\\\"\\n\\nSTEP 13: If both have nothing new, send both \\\"no new emails\\\" messages.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n        \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n        \"bestEffort\": false\n      },\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": false,\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777730290996,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 295346,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777733890996,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1777733891009\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777730586342\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"720739ac-4722-437b-8271-b7c1189c905c\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:cody:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Weather Cache Refresh\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774894946623,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 900000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1774894946623\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"main\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n        \"text\": \"Run this shell command and do NOT reply with anything else, just exit:\\n\\ncurl -s 'https://api.open-meteo.com/v1/forecast?latitude=35.96&longitude=-83.92&hourly=temperature_2m,weathercode,precipitation,windspeed_10m,uv_index,relativehumidity_2m&daily=temperature_2m_max,temperature_2m_min,weathercode,uv_index_max,precipitation_sum,sunrise,sunset&current_weather=true&forecast_days=3&temperature_unit=fahrenheit&windspeed_unit=mph&precipitation_unit=inch&timezone=America%2FNew_York' -o /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/.weather_cache.json 2>&1 && echo 'Weather cache updated'\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777734380090,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777733480090,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 5,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777733480095\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ecc194aa-784b-4fd8-bb18-7088d1077903\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Zyrtec Night Reminder\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775667349513,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 21 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"next-heartbeat\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Use the message tool to send exactly this ONE message to Telegram chat 8212808444 and nothing else: '🌙 Hey Bobby! Time to take your Zyrtec 💊'. Do not add any commentary, just send it.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 3600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777770000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777683600019,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 181861,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777683781880\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"3f20d0fb-bb39-4216-a3a2-d87613e075f4\",\n      \"name\": \"Memory Dreaming Promotion\",\n      \"description\": \"[managed-by=memory-core.short-term-promotion] Promote weighted short-term recalls into MEMORY.md (lim