{"type":"message","id":"b9a53ea8","parentId":"8453a637","timestamp":"2026-05-02T15:00:58.473Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done! I've updated the skill to include both Gmail and iCloud, and updated the cron job to use the skill. Let me give Bobby a summary.","thinkingSignature":"31e0d7b078eaaa4f843a6100f46adad78783f1ceceb80c0f3e39dfa1145ef50a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nDone! Updated both:\n\n**Skill** (`email-processor/SKILL.md`): Now handles both Gmail AND iCloud with the full label rules, interpretation logic, and processing steps — much cleaner than the old 13-step script.\n\n**Cron job** (`Emmy Email Check`): Now just says:\n> \"Run the email processor skill at ~/.openclaw/skills/email-processor/SKILL.md. Follow it exactly.\"\n\nPlus I added `timeoutSeconds: 300` to give it a comfortable window. The skill itself is lean and focused, so it should complete well within that time. The old run took ~4.9 minutes and actually succeeded — this new leaner version should be way faster."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":595,"output":180,"cacheRead":59360,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60135,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777734054783,"responseId":"064544a66dfefa1f8e752c659fabf09c"}}
