{"type":"message","id":"9b8ca39c","parentId":"d015b98f","timestamp":"2026-05-02T16:24:46.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me send the Gmail and iCloud reports to Bobby. I have 49 unread emails in Gmail (all before noon today), and iCloud has no new messages. But wait - the user asked for emails from the last hour. Let me think about what \"new\" means in this context.\n\nActually, the user said \"all new emails within the past hour since the last run\" - so since 11:58 AM. Let me check the emails that came in after 11:58 AM today:\n\nLooking at the Gmail list:\n- 19de8d22cfadb367 - Sat, 02 May 2026 13:13:00 +0000 (UTC) - 9:13 AM EDT - TikTok\n- 19de8915278a7aef - Sat, 02 May 2026 12:02:10 +0000 (UTC) - 8:02 AM EDT - Clipp.com\n\n\n- 19de7eb7af43961a - Sat, 2 May 2026 09:01:01 +0000 - 5:01 AM EDT - Affirm\n\nWait, I need to correct my timezone conversion - 12:02:10 UTC actually converts to 8:02 AM EDT, not after 11:58 AM. And 13:13:00 UTC is 9:13 AM EDT, so none of these recent emails actually came in after the 11:58 AM cutoff.\n\nBut the user has 49 unread emails, so I should report on all the unread ones regardless. For Gmail, the most recent messages are the TikTok and Clipp.com notifications, followed by the Affirm statement, Apple Music recap, Apple security alert, and X Developer Platform receipt. The iCloud account has no new messages - everything there is from late January through early May. I should organize these by priority: the Affirm payment due in 3 days and the Apple security alert are the most urgent, then the X Developer Platform charge, and the rest are lower priority promos and marketing. Since these are all pre-existing unread emails rather than new arrivals, I'll format them using the Gmail categories (Bills/Payments, Orders, Updates, Low Priority) and present them cleanly for the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"7063300bba78fd7f38f1ba6164cc5252399501e4e05cb86339e4deb0e9d37799"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nFair! Here's the full email check right now:\n\n**📬 GMAIL — 49 unread emails in your inbox** (oldest to newest, most recent first):\n\n🔴 **URGENT:**\n• **Affirm** — Payment due in 3 days\n  └ $129.59 payment due May 5, 2026\n• **Apple** — An app-specific password was generated for your Apple Account\n  └ ⚠️ Security alert — someone generated an app-specific password on your Apple account\n\n🟡 **IMPORTANT:**\n• **X Developer Platform** — Your X Developer Platform receipt [#1318-4669] — $10.00\n• **Affirm** — Your April Affirm Card statement is here\n• **Y-12 Credit Union** — Your Y-12 Credit Union eStatement Is Available\n• **Apple Music for Artists** — Bobby Galletta: Weekly Recap Apr 24-30\n\n⚪ **LOW PRIORITY:** (45 emails — newsletters, promos, marketing)\nTikTok, Clipp.com, Netflix, vidIQ, HP, iHeart Daily, Giacomo's Pizza, Broadway Direct, ZipRecruiter, PetScreening, Newspapers.com, USPS, Capital One, Uber Pro Card, Discover, Aventine, Doja Cat, YSL Beauty, Thomas Penninger, Rockstar, Slice, Historic Hudson Valley, Apotheca, and more\n\n**📬 ICLOUD — No new emails** (all 10 are older, already seen)\n\nThe timestamp is now updated. Cron will take over every hour from here. Let me know how the next few runs go!"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":199,"output":805,"cacheRead":104064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105068,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777739067015,"responseId":"0645583b882a07577ae2ffeafb4c7bc3"}}
