{"type":"message","id":"dd521e98","parentId":"6610064a","timestamp":"2026-05-02T17:08:19.837Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I reset the timestamp to now. But the next run is at 12:58 PM - which was 10 minutes ago! So the cron has already run. Let me check what happened.\n","thinkingSignature":"afc703896eb488442703ee5b9bda7087cc96c83f4585ef7587137857f8a3c5e0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThe cron already ran at **12:58 PM** (10 minutes ago) — that's when the timestamp got updated to 13:03. But you still got old emails, which means the timestamp comparison logic in the skill might not be working correctly.\n\nI just reset the timestamp to right now (13:08). The next run will be at **1:58 PM** and should catch truly new emails from this point forward.\n\nCan you check — do you have any emails that came into your Gmail AFTER 1:00 PM today?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":151,"cacheRead":105984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106244,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777741690840,"responseId":"0645627a638a95ae0aa3e5c69e1b43e4"}}
