{"type":"message","id":"ac4fcfd4","parentId":"fabb1afd","timestamp":"2026-05-02T18:18:40.940Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me explain to Bobby what I changed and when the next run is.\n","thinkingSignature":"92ee94532eb84d5789a4983ff1f817267a9ee5adcf79dfa52b8b1fd5f8e5ec28"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nYes, that makes total sense! I've updated the skill to check **the past 1-hour window** dynamically — at each run, it calculates \"1 hour ago from now\" and only shows emails received in that window.\n\n**How it works now:**\n- Cron fires at 2 PM\n- Skill calculates: \"1 hour ago = 1 PM\" \n- Shows only emails received between 1 PM - 2 PM\n- Timestamp file is still updated after each run, but the 1-hour window is calculated fresh each time\n\n**The next run is at ~3:00 PM** — it will check for emails from 2 PM to 3 PM. Let me know how it goes!"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1133,"output":164,"cacheRead":110656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111953,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777745915659,"responseId":"064572fb485a82d53a5b1f409e7e89d8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f70f0127","parentId":"ac4fcfd4","timestamp":"2026-05-02T18:21:33.337Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"So as you are reading the emails, are you marking them as read as well?"}],"timestamp":1777746093334}}
