{"type":"message","id":"8a402af1","parentId":"2d0ea98e","timestamp":"2026-05-02T18:24:01.395Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done! I sent both messages and updated the timestamps. Let me confirm to Bobby.","thinkingSignature":"677265506d8ef0ef16e4d3c5a3b85db8b9cdf24573efd8f7b2df305961d6098c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nDone! Just sent you **two separate Telegram messages:**\n\n1. **📬 GMAIL — All 50 unread emails** — organized by urgent/important/low priority with snippets\n2. **📬 ICLOUD — No new emails**\n\nAll timestamps are updated to now (2:24 PM). The hourly cron will now catch emails received from this point forward.\n\nFor the future hourly checks, I only report emails from the past hour — so anything truly NEW since the last run. The older unread ones will stay in your inbox but won't be re-reported unless they're still within the 1-hour window of a future run."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":151,"output":146,"cacheRead":120992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121289,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777746239153,"responseId":"0645743feef862db43134cc124686a91"}}
